      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented test suite covering hemolysis transport equations; independent code review completed.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (OpenFOAM v9) is version-controlled and a partial test suite exists covering basic fluid transport. However, hemolysis-specific transport equation verification tests are incomplete and no independent third-party code review has been performed. Achieved level 3 against required level 4 for MRL 5."
    },
    {
