      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy tests for all governing equations including hemolysis power-law transport; comparison against manufactured solutions.",
      "rationale": "Order-of-accuracy tests were performed for Navier-Stokes equations and confirmed second-order spatial convergence. The hemolysis power-law transport equation was not subjected to manufactured solution testing. Partial compliance yields achieved level 3; required level is 4 for Class III MRL 5 device."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
