      "rationale": "Comparison was performed against steady-state NIH measurements only. Agreement was within 18% but without uncertainty bounds on the experimental side. No pulsatile output comparison exists. The absence of pulsatile comparison data and the lack of experimental uncertainty quantification constrain the achieved level to 2 against required level 4."
    },
    {
