      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities performed on geometrically similar pump under pulsatile VAD flow conditions; operating points span the full COU envelope.",
      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry under steady-state conditions. The COU specifies pulsatile VAD operation. The geometric similarity is acceptable, but the flow regime mismatch means validation activities do not adequately cover the COU. No pulsatile validation activity exists. Achieved level 1 against required level 4 — the largest single credibility gap in this assessment."
    },
    {
