      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ was performed but input distributions for blood rheology parameters were taken from literature rather than device-specific clinical measurements. Inlet pulsatile waveform uncertainty was not included in the Monte Carlo analysis. Flagged as epistemic gap; not-assessed for full MRL 5 requirements. Achieved level 2."
