      "rationale": "The FDA benchmark dataset does not provide individual sample-level characterisation of blood analogue properties. Hematocrit is reported as a nominal value only. No minimum sample size analysis was performed for the statistical comparison. Flagged as epistemic gap. Achieved level 1."
